pageBody: This project started as a collaboration between the founders of Insight Fit, Lead Robot, and Sigma Digital.We all felt the need to act, and to contribute. Reaching out to our collective networks, we found that many others were excited to do something that could help during the COVID 19 global crisis. If you'd like to help fight COVID-19 fill out the form above, and If you're a developer, head on over to our [open source project on GitHub.](https://github.com/Insight-fit-open-source "Insight Fit Open Source")
